thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by ELLEN

author: ELLEN
title: ELLEN
text: Good service the car was an up to date model very clean and easy to drive. I felt I was well informed by the staff of the policies of hiring and returning the car. Very happy that it's the only company that allows you to hire a car on your p plates. I would recommend to anyone.
